  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Enrolled Nurse",
  "description": "<p><u>Clinical Care</u></p>\n<p>a. Assists the registered nurses in the delivery of nursing care to the residents in the Home.</p>\n<p>b. Assists the registered nurse in the supervision of nursing aides and health attendants</p>\n<p>c. Perform all nursing procedures which include administration of medications, wound dressing and meal feeding.</p>\n<p>d. Ensures the comfort and good personal hygiene of the residents under her/his care, e.g. bed bath/shower bath, changing of clothes and bed sheets and tidiness of the room.</p>\n<p>e. Identify symptoms of residents that are related to illnesses and/or decline in functional and cognitive abilities and advocate early medical attention.</p>\n<p><u>Training and Development</u></p>\n<p>f. Mentor and guide nursing aides and healthcare attendants in performing their functional duties.</p>\n<p>g. Attend upgrading programs to keep abreast with clinical knowledge and to develop work-required skills.</p>\n<p><u>Administration</u></p>\n<p>h. Educate family members of residents on their health conditions and help them gain understanding on the holistic care provided.</p>\n<p>i. Ensure all documentation of residents’ case is maintained appropriately.</p>\n<p><u>Ad-hoc Duties</u></p>\n<p>· Any other tasks assigned by Nurse Manager/Assistant Director of Nursing from time to time.</p>",
